name: ModeratorPurchaseContract

methods.name: create_moderator
methods.desc: Initialize moderator with pricing in ALGO

methods.name: buyout_moderator
methods.desc: Transfer permanent ownership with 90/10 revenue split

methods.name: update_pricing
methods.desc: Update pricing - only current owner can call

methods.name: use_hourly_access
methods.desc: Deduct hours from user's hourly access

methods.name: get_moderator_info
methods.desc: Get pricing and ownership info (read-only, no cost)

methods.name: get_user_access
methods.desc: Get user's access details (read-only, no cost)

methods.name: has_valid_access
methods.desc: Check if user has valid access (read-only, no cost)

desc:
Smart contract for moderator purchases with 3 access types:
    1. Hourly access (pay per hour)
    2. Monthly license (subscription)
    3. Buyout (permanent ownership)
    
    Based on citadel-algo library patterns with 90/10 revenue split.

sourceInfo.errorMessage: can only call when not creating
